    </title>

	<description>
        <en>
<![CDATA[This is the DAF trailer pack. It belongs to the DAF 105 XF, but you can also use it to any other vehicle if you want.
You can choose between 3 different axles, except for the short one.
The back axle is liftable with every configuration you like and if you choose to play with 3 axels the front axle is also liftable, except for the short one.
All the trailers have AutoLoad functions.
All the trailers have loading ramps for vehicles.

Price: 20000€ - 35000€
Brand: DAF
-Wheel Configurations
-Color Configurations
-RimColor Configurations
-Liftable axles
-Ramps
-AutoLoad

Changelog 2.0.0.0:
 - Fixed flying/driving backwards issue
 - Fixed minor issues
 - Optimized File
]]>
		</en>
    </description>
